title: Green Lantern 79 + 80 (1996-10) (OkC.O.M.P.U.T.O.-Novus-HD)
description:
A Novus Release

========================================================


Green Lantern 79 + 80 (1996-10)


#79  Sonar, the Neron-enhanced metahuman who was defeated before by the combined power of Green Lantern and Flash, is back for revenge, and he has control of the island prison filled with super-villains known as the Slab.

#80  Trapped long ago, the original, villainous Dr. Light emerges from Green Lantern's power battery, more powerful than ever with total control over Kyle Rayner's emerald energy creations.[/quote]  


Thanks goes to OkC.O.M.P.U.T.O for this release.
